source/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"/ 6:07 PM\", \"from\": 33, \"to\": 42}, {\"ngram\": \"criminal complaints\", \"from\": 117, \"to\": 136}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 184, \"to\": 192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Swiss-based IOC allowing female boxers Imane Khelif and Lin Yu-ting to compete and win gold medals in Paris last year \\\"may serve as grounds for criminal prosecution,\\\" the Russian-led IBA claimed in a statement.\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 435, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 237, \"end\": 240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3440083940041952e-40, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 264, \"end\": 276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 281, \"end\": 292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}, {\"begin\": 327, \"end\": 332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999810920601, \"rank\": 1.8908159992580125e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 408, \"end\": 411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\":